 R←Test_ReplaceVars_002(stopFlag batchFlag);n;Text;n2;⎕TRAP;buffer
⍝ Replace string in string & in vector of vectors by shorter string. Other variables must remain unchanged.
 ⎕TRAP←(999 'C' '. ⍝ Deliberate error')(0 'N')
 R←∆Failed

⍝ Preconditions
 1 #._Fire.Fire.Run 0
 n←#._Fire.Fire.GUI.n
 ∆InitialyzeFireMainGUI_Settings n

 #.⎕SHADOW'TEMP'
 '#.TEMP'⎕NS''
 #.TEMP.varsSimple←'APL is REALLY great'
 #.TEMP.varsNested←'APL is REALLY great' 'It really is!' 'Yes, APL is REALLY great'
 #.TEMP.varsMatrix←⊃'APL is REALLY great' 'It really is!' 'Yes, APL is REALLY great'
 #.TEMP.varsMixed←'APL is REALLY great' 'It really is!' 'Yes, APL is REALLY great' 1

 n.SearchFor.Text←'is REALLY great'
 n.LookIn.Text←'#.TEMP'

 {}∆Select n.StartBtn
 ∆Process n.Form
 →GoToTidyUp 4≠⍴n.HitList.Items

 {}∆Select n.ReplaceBtn
 ∆Process n.Form

 n2←#._Fire.Fire.Replace.n
 ∆InitialyzeFireReplaceGUI_Settings n2
 n2.ReplaceBy.Text←'is great'

 {}∆Select n2.StartBtn
 ∆Process n.Form
 →GoToTidyUp 2≠#._Fire.Fire.Replace.NoOfReplacements
 →GoToTidyUp'APL is great' 'It really is!' 'Yes, APL is great'≢#.TEMP.varsNested
 →GoToTidyUp'APL is great'≢#.TEMP.varsSimple
 →GoToTidyUp(⊃'APL is REALLY great' 'It really is!' 'Yes, APL is REALLY great')≢#.TEMP.varsMatrix
 →GoToTidyUp'APL is REALLY great' 'It really is!' 'Yes, APL is REALLY great' 1≢#.TEMP.varsMixed
 R←∆OK

∆TidyUp:
 CloseFire
